title: The grand designs of the papists, in the reign of our late sovereign, Charles the I and now carried on against His Present Majesty, his government, and the Protestant religion.
author: Prynne, William, 1600-1669.
notes: Part of the letters and text in English and Latin.
Written by William Prynne. Cf. BM; Wing (2nd ed.).
Includes letters by Ondrej Habervesl z Habernfeldu and Sir William Boswell.
Reproduction of original in Union Theological Seminary Library, New York.
